main event: An unidentified aerial phenomenon was observed moving at high speed in Shiraz, Iran, from 23-29 September 1962.
interesting points: The object exhibited behavior of contracting and expanding in size.,The object made a whooshing sound as it moved.,The observation lasted for 3-4 minutes.,The Air Force investigator noted that the motion was consistent with a satellite or missile but the sound was unusual., Several people were involved in witnessing the event and local military authorities were notified.
witness description: unspecified individuals who observed the object
